WEBVTT

00:04:27.026 --> 00:04:30.748
men yangi mavjudodlar hayoti haqida 
topganimda juda ham hayajonda edim.

00:04:30.772 --> 00:04:32.548
Men dadamni oldiga bordim va

00:04:32.572 --> 00:04:35.990
"Dada. men mavjudodlarning yangi turlarini
topdim" dedim.

00:04:36.574 --> 00:04:38.075
U kulib,

00:04:38.099 --> 00:04:41.367
"Bu yahshi. Men o'ylaymanki sen ularga 
davo ham topding" dedi.

00:04:41.391 --> 00:04:42.837
(Kulgu)

00:04:42.861 --> 00:04:44.033
"Buni davolash."

00:04:45.202 --> 00:04:47.909
Hozir dadam meni eng katta muxlisim,

00:04:47.933 --> 00:04:52.303
shuning uchun u mening yangi hayot 
shaklini o'ldirishni xohlagan payti

00:04:52.327 --> 00:04:54.873
men uni farzand va olim sifatida

00:04:54.897 --> 00:04:57.058
uyaltirib qo'yganimni anglab yetdim.

00:04:57.082 --> 00:05:01.008
Labaratoriyalarda hamda odamlarning 
bog'ida ishlab yurgan